<section id="To_delete_one_snapshot" remap="TID_14866">
	<title>Deleting a Snapshot</title>
	<para> 
		<productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> enables you to delete snapshots when you no longer need them.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Delete a Snapshot</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				From <menuchoice><guimenu>Infrastructure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Virtual Machines</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, click on the virtual machine that you want to remove the snapshot from.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				From the <guilabel>Properties</guilabel> area, click <guilabel>Snapshots</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select the snapshot that you want to remove.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1861.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Delete Snapshots</guilabel>), and then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1861.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Delete Selected Snapshot</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to confirm.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>